#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "[[!meta title=\"Resetting a USB stick using macOS\"]]\n"
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Uninstalling Tails using macOS\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\" Einen USB-Stick oder eine SD-Karte unter macOS zurücksetzen\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "[[!inline pages=\"doc/reset.intro\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"
msgid "[[!inline pages=\"doc/first_steps/uninstall.intro\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!inline pages=\"doc/reset.intro.de\" raw=\"yes\" sort=\"age\"]]\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Start on macOS."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Make sure that the USB stick that you want to reset is unplugged."
msgid "Make sure that the USB stick that you want to uninstall is unplugged."
msgstr ""
"Stellen Sie sicher, dass der USB-Stick, den Sie zurücksetzen möchten, nicht "
"angeschlossen ist."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Start *Disk Utility*."
msgstr "Starten Sie das *Festplattendienstprogramm*."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   A list of all the storage devices on the computer appears in the left pane\n"
"   of the window.\n"
msgstr "   Eine Liste aller Speichermedien des Computers erscheint im linken Bereich des Fensters.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Plug in the USB stick that you want to reset."
msgid "Plug in the USB stick that you want to uninstall."
msgstr "Schließen Sie den USB-Stick, den Sie zurücksetzen möchten, an."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   A new device appears in the list of storage devices. This new device\n"
"   corresponds to the USB stick that you plugged in. Click on it.\n"
msgstr ""
"   Ein neues Medium erscheint in der Liste der Speichermedien. Dieses Medium\n"
"   entspricht dem USB-Stick, den Sie angeschlossen haben. Wählen Sie ihn aus.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "In the list of storage devices, verify that the device corresponds to the "
#| "USB stick that you want to reset, its brand, its size, etc."
msgid ""
"In the list of storage devices, verify that the device corresponds to the "
"USB stick that you want to uninstall, its brand, its size, etc."
msgstr ""
"Überprüfen Sie in der Liste der Speichermedien, ob das Gerät dem USB-Stick "
"entspricht, den Sie zurücksetzen möchten, sowie dessen Marke, Größe usw."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   <div class=\"caution\">\n"
msgstr "   <div class=\"caution\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "<p><b>You might overwrite any hard disk on the computer.</b></p>\n"
msgid "   <p>You might overwrite any hard disk on the computer.</p>\n"
msgstr "<p><b>Sie könnten jegliche Festplatten des Computers überschreiben.</b></p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "<p>If at some point you are not sure about which device to choose, stop proceeding.</p>\n"
msgid "   <p>If you are not sure about which device to choose, stop proceeding.</p>\n"
msgstr "<p>Falls Sie sich an irgendeinem Punkt unsicher darüber sind, welches Medium Sie wählen sollen, brechen Sie den Vorgang ab.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   </div>\n"
msgstr "   </div>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "   b. If there is an **Erase**\n"
#| "   button on the top middle, click on it.\n"
msgid "To reset the USB stick, select the **Erase** button in the top middle."
msgstr ""
"   b. Wenn es oben in der Mitte einen <span class=\"bold\">\n"
"    Löschen</span>-Knopf gibt, klicke darauf.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "In the confirmation dialog, click on the **Erase** button to confirm."
msgstr ""
"Wählen Sie im Bestätigungs-Dialogfenster die Schaltfläche <span "
"class=\"bold\">Löschen</span> aus, um zu bestätigen."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"In the **Erase** dialog, if you want the USB stick to also work on Windows "
"and Linux, specify:"
msgstr ""
"Im **Löschen**-Dialog, wenn Sie möchten, dass der USB-Stick auch unter "
"Windows und Linux funktioniert, geben Sie Folgendes an:"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid "**Format**: **MS-DOS (FAT)**"
msgstr "**Format**: **MS-DOS (FAT)**"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
msgid "**Scheme**: **Master Boot Record**"
msgstr "**Scheme**: **Master Boot Record**"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Click **Erase**."
msgstr "Klicken Sie auf **Löschen**."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"note\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"note\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>If the erase process fails, try [[!toggle id=\"format\"\n"
"text=\"formatting the USB stick using the command line\"]] first.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>Wenn der Löschvorgang fehlschlägt, versuchen Sie zuerst [[!toggle id=\"format\" \n"
"text=\"den USB-Stick über die Befehlszeile zu formatieren\"]].</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!toggleable id=\"format\" text=\"\"\"\n"
msgstr "[[!toggleable id=\"format\" text=\"\"\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<span class=\"hide\">[[!toggle id=\"format\" text=\"\"]]</span>\n"
msgstr "<span class=\"hide\">[[!toggle id=\"format\" text=\"\"]]</span>\n"

#. type: Title -
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "Resetting a USB stick using the command line"
msgid "Formatting the USB stick using the command line"
msgstr "Zurücksetzen eines USB-Sticks über die Befehlszeile"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<!-- Note for translators: This section is very similar to /install/inc/steps/install_with_etcher.inline. -->\n"
msgstr "<!-- Note for translators: This section is very similar to /install/inc/steps/install_with_etcher.inline. -->\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Unplug the USB stick from the computer."
msgstr "Ziehen Sie den USB-Stick vom Computer ab."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Open the **Terminal** utility from **Applications**&nbsp;▸ **Utilities**."
msgid "Open the **Terminal** utility from **Applications&nbsp;▸ Utilities**."
msgstr ""
"Öffnen Sie das **Terminal**-Dienstprogramm über **Anwendungen** &nbsp;▸ "
"**Dienstprogramme**."

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Execute the following command."
msgstr "Führen Sie den folgenden Befehl aus."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   <p class=\"command\">diskutil list</p>\n"
msgstr "   <p class=\"command\">diskutil list</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   It returns a list of the storage devices on the system. For example:\n"
msgstr "   Es wird eine Liste der Speichermedien des Systems ausgegeben. Zum Beispiel:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"       /dev/disk0\n"
"        #:                     TYPE NAME         SIZE      IDENTIFIER\n"
"        0:    GUID_partition_scheme             *500.1 GB  disk0\n"
"        1:                      EFI              209.7 MB  disk0s1\n"
"        2:                Apple_HFS MacDrive     250.0 GB  disk0s2\n"
"        3:                      EFI              134.1 GB  disk0s3\n"
"        4:     Microsoft Basic Data BOOTCAMP     115.5 GB  disk0s4\n"
msgstr ""
"       /dev/disk0\n"
"        #:                     TYPE NAME         SIZE      IDENTIFIER\n"
"        0:    GUID_partition_scheme             *500.1 GB  disk0\n"
"        1:                      EFI              209.7 MB  disk0s1\n"
"        2:                Apple_HFS MacDrive     250.0 GB  disk0s2\n"
"        3:                      EFI              134.1 GB  disk0s3\n"
"        4:     Microsoft Basic Data BOOTCAMP     115.5 GB  disk0s4\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Execute again the same command."
msgstr "Führen Sie den Befehl erneut aus."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   Your USB stick appears as a new device in the list. Check\n"
"   that its size corresponds to the size of your USB stick.\n"
msgstr ""
"   Ihr USB-Stick erscheint als neues Speichermedium in der Liste. Stellen Sie\n"
"   sicher, dass die Größe der Speicherkapazität Ihres USB-Sticks entspricht.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"       /dev/disk1\n"
"        #:                     TYPE NAME         SIZE      IDENTIFIER\n"
"        0:   FDisk_partition_scheme             *8.0 GB    disk1\n"
"        1:                Apple_HFS Untitled 1   8.0 GB    disk1s1\n"
msgstr ""
"       /dev/disk1\n"
"        #:                     TYPE NAME         SIZE      IDENTIFIER\n"
"        0:   FDisk_partition_scheme             *8.0 GB    disk1\n"
"        1:                Apple_HFS Untitled 1   8.0 GB    disk1s1\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid "Take note of the device name of your USB stick."
msgstr "Notieren Sie sich den Gerätenamen Ihres USB-Sticks."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   In this example, the USB stick is 8.0 GB and its device name is <span class=\"command-placeholder\">/dev/disk1</span>.\n"
"   Yours might be different.\n"
msgstr ""
"   In diesem Beispiel hat der USB-Stick eine Größe von 8,0 GB und sein Gerätename ist <span class=\"command-placeholder\">/dev/disk1</span>. \n"
" Ihr Gerätename könnte anders sein.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "<p>If at some point you are not sure about which device to choose, stop proceeding.</p>\n"
msgid "   <p>If you are not sure about the device, stop proceeding.</p>\n"
msgstr "<p>Falls Sie sich an irgendeinem Punkt unsicher darüber sind, welches Medium Sie wählen sollen, brechen Sie den Vorgang ab.</p>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Execute the following command to safely eject the USB stick. Replace <span "
"class=\"command-placeholder\">device</span> with the device name found in "
"step 6."
msgstr ""
"Führen Sie den folgenden Befehl aus, um den USB-Stick sicher auszuwerfen. "
"Ersetzen Sie <span class=\"command-placeholder\">device</span> durch den "
"Gerätenamen, der in Schritt 6 gefunden wurde."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   <p class=\"command-template\">diskutil unmountDisk <span class=\"command-placeholder\">device</span></p>\n"
msgstr "   <p class=\"command-template\">diskutil unmountDisk <span class=\"command-placeholder\">device</span></p>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Execute the following command to format the USB stick. Replace <span "
"class=\"command-placeholder\">device</span> with the device name found in "
"step 6."
msgstr ""
"Führen Sie den folgenden Befehl aus, um den USB-Stick zu formatieren. "
"Ersetzen Sie <span class=\"command-placeholder\">device</span> durch den "
"Gerätenamen, der in Schritt 6 gefunden wurde."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   <p class=\"command-template\">sudo fdisk -iy <span class=\"command-placeholder\">device</span></p>\n"
msgstr "   <p class=\"command-template\">sudo fdisk -iy <span class=\"command-placeholder\">device</span></p>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You can try to reset the USB stick again using *Disk Utility* from the "
#| "beginning of this page."
msgid ""
"You can try to uninstall the USB stick again using *Disk Utility* from the "
"beginning of this page."
msgstr ""
"Sie können versuchen, den USB-Stick erneut über <span "
"class=\"application\">Festplattendienstprogramm</span> von Anfang dieser "
"Seite zurückzusetzen."

